16
00:01:48,687 --> 00:01:50,900
♪I was told that the sky in my memories
is about to dawn♪

17
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:54,239
Struggle to choose
between Gu Shizhen and me?

18
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:59,450
♪Only fragments of light
are left to trace your shape♪

19
