♪Sunlight replays♪

203
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:39,860
♪When flowers
fall on the roadside again♪

204
00:19:40,225 --> 00:19:46,665
♪It's yesterday's color♪

205
00:19:48,012 --> 00:19:53,132
♪Who promised whom♪

206
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:59,112
♪Who escaped with whom♪

207
00:20:00,925 --> 00:20:06,085
♪The vortex
that confuses time and space♪

208
00:20:06,162 --> 00:20:13,442
♪Looking back at you and me♪
